window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A <b>small town friends to lovers murder mystery romance</b> from USA Today bestselling author Dakota Davies.</p> <p>Attending my best friend Noah’s wedding last summer was both the best thing and the worst thing to ever happen to me. The best was meeting Cora Tucker, Noah’s feisty little sister. That night we danced, laughed ourselves silly, and shared our dreams. Though we both knew it was just friendship, our chemistry crackled like a lit fuse.</p> <p>Not kissing her was the worst thing that could have happened to me. That and saying goodbye.</p> <p>So when my sheriff resigns in the middle of a high-stakes murder case and I’m suddenly a candidate for his replacement, there’s only one person I trust to help me win. Two days after my desperate call, Cora shows up looking as beautiful and confident as ever. Yet it’s clear this idea I hatched is making us miserable—me for having to resist the sassy spitfire, and Cora for inheriting an impossible campaign, and an impossible boss.</p> <p>But as our passion for each other flares to life, the criminal forces at work in my valley are watching, and they don’t like what they see…</p> <p><i>If you like a twisty mystery intertwined with sexy, spicy small town suspense, you will love Cora &amp; Seth's high-octane romance set in small town Alaska!</i></p> <p><b>Start listening to Her Wild Coast Promise today!</b></p> <p><i>Author's note: this story completes the Wild Hearts small town romantic suspense series featuring the hunky men in uniform of Storm Harbor. Enjoy it as a stand-alone or binge the whole series starting with book 1, Her Wild Coast Outlaw.</i></p>"; 
